bisq.core.dao.node.full

Class FullNodeExecutor

  • java.lang.Object
    • bisq.core.dao.node.full.FullNodeExecutor

  • public class FullNodeExecutor
extends java.lang.Object
    Processes tasks in custom thread. Results are mapped back to user thread so client don't need to deal with threading. We use a SingleThreadExecutor to guarantee that the parser is only running from one thread at a time to avoid risks with concurrent write to the BsqBlockChain.
